<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DNASPEC - 定性定量融合的综合集成研讨厅系统</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3c72 0%, #2a5298 100%);
            background-attachment: fixed;
        }

        .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8e44ad 0%, #3498db 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 5rem 0;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        header:before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 40px 40px;
            opacity: 0.3;
        }

        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #f1c40f, #e74c3c);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto 2rem;
            color: #ecf0f1;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #bdc3c7;
            font-style: italic;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        nav {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85);
            padding: 1.2rem 0;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            list-style: none;
        }

        .nav-links li {
            margin: 0.4rem 0.9rem;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
            padding: 0.7rem 1.4rem;
            border-radius: 30px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        main {
            min-height: calc(100vh - 200px);
        }

        .section {
            padding: 6rem 0;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96);
        }

        .section:nth-child(even) {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
        }

        .section h2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
            color: #2c3e50;
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 1.8rem;
        }

        .section h2:after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 140px;
            height: 6px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #f1c40f, #e67e22, #e74c3c, #9b59b6);
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .intro {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto 3rem;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .qualitative-quantitative {
            background: #f5f7fa;
        }

        .q2-model {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr 1fr;
            gap: 3rem;
            margin: 4rem 0;
        }

        .qualitative-side {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
        }

        .quantitative-side {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4facfe 0%, #00f2fe 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(79, 172, 254, 0.4);
        }

        .integration-center {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #43e97b 0%, #38f9d7 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(67, 233, 123, 0.4);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .integration-center h4 {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
        }

        .integration-center p {
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .conceptual-approach {
            background-color: white;
        }

        .approach-stages {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 4rem;
        }

        .approach-stage {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            border-left: 7px solid #3498db;
            transition: transform 0.4s ease, box-shadow 0.4s ease;
        }

        .approach-stage:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .approach-stage h3 {
            color: #2980b9;
            margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .approach-stage h3:before {
            content: '';
            display: inline-block;
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            background: #3498db;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }

        .approach-stage p {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #555;
        }

        .approach-stage ul {
            margin-left: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .approach-stage li {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #666;
        }

        .skills-application {
            background: #ecf0f1;
        }

        .skills-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 3rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .skill-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            border-left: 6px solid #9b59b6;
            transition: transform 0.4s ease;
        }

        .skill-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
        }

        .skill-card h3 {
            color: #8e44ad;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.7rem;
        }

        .skill-card h4 {
            color: #e74c3c;
            margin: 1.8rem 0 0.8rem 0;
        }

        .skill-card p {
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #555;
        }

        .skill-card ul {
            margin-left: 1.8rem;
        }

        .skill-card li {
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .workflow-section {
            background-color: white;
        }

        .workflow-steps {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 4rem 0;
        }

        .step {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            padding: 2rem;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            border-left: 5px solid #f39c12;
        }

        .step.reverse {
            flex-direction: row-reverse;
        }

        .step-number {
            width: 70px;
            height: 70px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f39c12, #e67e22);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            margin: 0 2rem;
        }

        .step-content {
            flex-grow: 1;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .step-content h4 {
            color: #d35400;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
        }

        .integration-patterns {
            background: #f5f7fa;
        }

        .pattern-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2.5rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .pattern-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 2.8rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 5px solid #2ecc71;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .pattern-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
        }

        .pattern-card h3 {
            color: #27ae60;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .pattern-card p {
            color: #7f8c8d;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .future-vision {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8e44ad 0%, #3498db 100%);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 6rem 0;
        }

        .future-vision h2 {
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        }

        .future-vision p {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto 2rem;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .vision-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 2.5rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .vision-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .vision-card h3 {
            color: #f1c40f;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
        }

        .summary-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2980b9 0%, #8e44ad 100%);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 6rem 0;
        }

        .summary-section h2 {
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .summary-section p {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto 2rem;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .page-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 1.8rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .page-link {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f1c40f, #e67e22);
            color: white;
            padding: 0.9rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(241, 196, 15, 0.3);
        }

        .page-link:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(241, 196, 15, 0.5);
        }

        footer {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50 0%, #34495e 100%);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3.5rem 0;
        }

        .footer-content p {
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .example-box {
            background-color: #e8f4fd;
            padding: 1.8rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 1.8rem 0;
            border-left: 5px solid #3498db;
        }

        .example-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2980b9;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        }

        .phase-label {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin: 0.5rem 0.8rem 0.8rem 0;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }

            header p {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }

            .section h2 {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }

            .nav-links {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }

            .nav-links li {
                margin: 0.4rem 0;
            }

            .q2-model {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .step {
                flex-direction: column !important;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .step-number {
                margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
            }

            .step-content {
                text-align: center;
            }

            .page-links {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>DNASPEC综合集成研讨厅</h1>
            <p>定性定量融合的AI原生系统架构 - 从简单Idea到复杂智能系统的智能化自动增长平台</p>
            <p class="subtitle">以格式塔认知原则为指导，实现智能与确定性的平衡</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="#intro">理念概述</a></li>
            <li><a href="#q2-model">定性定量模型</a></li>
            <li><a href="#approach">概念性方法</a></li>
            <li><a href="#skills">技能应用</a></li>
            <li><a href="#workflow">工作流整合</a></li>
            <li><a href="#patterns">集成模式</a></li>
            <li><a href="#vision">未来愿景</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <main>
        <!-- 理念概述 -->
        <section id="intro" class="section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>定性定量综合集成研讨厅核心理念</h2>
                <div class="intro">
                    <p>在AI原生时代，每个系统都将是综合集成研讨厅 - 一种融合定性定量两种处理方式的智能系统。这种架构以生物DNA为灵感，将确定性逻辑通过代码固化，将不确定性分析通过智能体处理，将模糊决策以最直观的形式呈现给用户界面，实现真正的智能化自动增长。</p>
                    <p>本系统遵循认知过程的格式塔原则，通过局部智能体架构避免全局上下文膨胀，通过宪法需求管理确保系统一致性，通过分级审核机制实现多层级对齐，确保系统从简单Idea到复杂智能体的平稳演进。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 定性定量模型 -->
        <section id="q2-model" class="section qualitative-quantitative">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>定性定量融合模型</h2>
                <p class="intro">综合集成研讨厅采用定性定量分层处理，二者通过智能接口协同工作，形成统一连贯的智能体体验</p>

                <div class="q2-model">
                    <div class="qualitative-side">
                        <h4>定性处理层</h4>
                        <p>思维链推理 (Chain of Thought)</p>
                        <p>提示词优化</p>
                        <p>置信度审核</p>
                        <p>多源多维度思考</p>
                        <p>共识计算</p>
                        <p>用户意图理解</p>
                        <p>创造性分析</p>
                        <p>智能决策支持</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="integration-center">
                        <h4>智能接口层</h4>
                        <p>定性定量协同</p>
                        <p>任务分配与路由</p>
                        <p>智能决策融合</p>
                        <p>用户意图解析</p>
                        <p>不确定性评估</p>
                        <p>结果反馈机制</p>
                        <p>上下文管理</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="quantitative-side">
                        <h4>定量处理层</h4>
                        <p>算法模块</p>
                        <p>数据处理</p>
                        <p>逻辑验证</p>
                        <p>性能计算</p>
                        <p>确定性逻辑</p>
                        <p>代码执行</p>
                        <p>标准化接口</p>
                        <p>可预测行为</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="example-box">
                    <div class="example-title">定性定量融合示例:</div>
                    <p>当用户提出"创建一个智能推荐系统"的需求时：</p>
                    <p><strong>定性部分:</strong> 分析用户意图，理解推荐需求的多样性，应用链式思维分解推荐逻辑，生成认知框架</p>
                    <p><strong>定量部分:</strong> 实现具体的推荐算法，执行确定性计算，管理数据结构和性能优化</p>
                    <p><strong>接口层:</strong> 协调定性分析结果与定量计算实现，处理推荐逻辑中不确定的部分，反馈给用户界面进行确认</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 概念性方法 -->
        <section id="approach" class="section conceptual-approach">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>概念性方法：从简单到复杂的渐进式增长</h2>
                <div class="approach-stages">
                    <div class="approach-stage">
                        <h3>阶段1：Idea初始阶段 - 意图理解与澄清</h3>
                        <p>系统接收用户的原始想法和概念。此阶段的重点是通过定性处理理解用户意图，并使用定量处理验证概念的可行性。上下文分析技能确保输入清晰度，认知模板技能应用链式思维分解模糊概念。</p>
                        
                        <p><strong>定性处理:</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>理解用户模糊意图</li>
                            <li>应用认知框架结构化概念</li>
                            <li>探索概念的可能性空间</li>
                            <li>生成初步的定性评估</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <p><strong>定量处理:</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>验证概念的技术可行性</li>
                            <li>评估资源需求</li>
                            <li>生成量化指标</li>
                            <li>确定实现的确定性部分</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <p><strong>技能应用:</strong> <span class="phase-label">Idea阶段</span> /dnaspec.context-analysis, <span class="phase-label">Idea阶段</span> /dnaspec.cognitive-template</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="approach-stage">
                        <h3>阶段2：需求精细化阶段 - 宪法确立与约束生成</h3>
                        <p>将概念转化为规范化的需求，并建立宪法版本管理。此阶段通过约束生成技能锁定初始需求宪法，确保后续发展不偏离初心。上下文优化技能精炼需求描述，架构师技能设计可扩展架构。</p>
                        
                        <p><strong>定性处理:</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>深化需求理解</li>
                            <li>识别需求中的不确定性</li>
                            <li>生成需求的定性模型</li>
                            <li>确定用户界面交互模式</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <p><strong>定量处理:</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>建立需求版本管理系统</li>
                            <li>生成具体的约束定义</li>
                            <li>设计系统架构的定量参数</li>
                            <li>确定性能和安全指标</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <p><strong>技能应用:</strong> <span class="phase-label">需求阶段</span> /dnaspec.constraint-generator, <span class="phase-label">需求阶段</span> /dnaspec.architect, <span class="phase-label">需求阶段</span> /dnaspec.context-optimization</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="approach-stage">
                        <h3>阶段3：功能细化与模块化阶段 - 任务分解与隔离</h3>
                        <p>将需求分解为具体的可执行模块，实现模块化设计。通过任务分解技能基于设计原则分解任务，为每个任务创建独立工作区，实现上下文隔离，防止任务爆炸。</p>
                        
                        <p><strong>定性处理:</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>确定模块的职责边界</li>
                            <li>分析模块间的交互模式</li>
                            <li>设计模块的智能接口</li>
                            <li>评估模块化的合理性</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <p><strong>定量处理:</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>生成具体的模块分解方案</li>
                            <li>确定模块间的接口协议</li>
                            <li>测量模块复杂度和依赖关系</li>
                            <li>验证模块化原则的实现</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <p><strong>技能应用:</strong> <span class="phase-label">细化阶段</span> /dnaspec.task-decomposer, <span class="phase-label">细化阶段</span> /dnaspec.modulizer, <span class="phase-label">细化阶段</span> /dnaspec.workspace</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="approach-stage">
                        <h3>阶段4：智能体集成与协同阶段 - 局部智能与系统协调</h3>
                        <p>创建局部智能体处理复杂任务，实现智能体社会架构。通过智能体创建技能创建专业智能体，API检查技能验证智能体接口一致性，工作流技能管理智能体协作。</p>
                        
                        <p><strong>定性处理:</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>设计智能体的职责分工</li>
